---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kishki â€” Lina" bgColor="#F5F5F0">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">

    <!-- Header image -->
    <img src="/kishki/IMG_0106.jpeg" alt="Kishki" class="w-full mb-10" />

    <!-- Title -->
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900" style="font-size: 32px;">Kishki</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-3 mb-10">
      The story begins with a 10 year old girl who opens a mysterious gift from her late mother. Ends up with a magical never ending scarf that dominates her school, house, neighborhood, city, and her whole world. How will she escape this blessing that turned out to be a dilemma.
    </p>

    <!-- Book pages -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <img src="/kishki/6_Eng_page.jpg" alt="Kishki book page" class="w-full mb-4" />
      <img src="/kishki/10eng_page.jpg" alt="Kishki book page" class="w-full mb-4" />
      <img src="/kishki/11_Eng_page.jpg" alt="Kishki book page" class="w-full mb-4" />
    </section>

    <!-- Sketch to Reality -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Sketch to Reality</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-6">
        My design process always starts with a sketch, 100s of sketches to be honest. Then, I moved on to testing it with several children to see if it is appealing to them. I then move to transferring the sketch onto the fabric.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mb-6">
        The full drawing embroidery takes around 3 days or maybe more depending on how complex the drawing is. First starting with just the line art, and then the coloring.
      </p>
      <img src="/kishki/IMG_0501.jpeg" alt="Embroidery process" class="w-full mb-4" />
    </section>

    <!-- Embroidery video -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <video
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        class="w-full"
      >
        <source
          src="https://video.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6391d1fed9ccd1251ba2135c/5627d747-4f5f-4b99-b0c9-1fad156ac5de/playlist.m3u8"
          type="application/x-mpegURL"
        />
      </video>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3" style="font-size: 20px;">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">
        Get in touch with me, if you liked the concept, and story of the book. I would love to work together to get it published!
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
